 PM2.5\nexposure. The purpose of this project was to analyze PM2.5 mean concentration\nacross America to identify and quantify any pollution episodes, as well as try\nto explain their dynamics using large scale, meteorological processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Nov 2022 18:49:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Nov 2022 16:01:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 16 Dec 2022 15:05:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-19"}
